<h2 class="node__title node-title"><a href="/blog/abortion-guns-are-two-hardest-issues-discuss-here-s-why">Abortion &amp; Guns Are Two of the Hardest Issues to Discuss. Here’s Why.</a></h2>
<div class="submitted-category">Common Ground / September 26th, 2023 / By <a href="/news-source/jess-carpenter-media-bias">Jessica Carpenter</a>                </div>

<div class="row-fluid">
      <div class="span4"><img typeof="foaf:Image" src="https://www.allsides.com/sites/default/files/styles/blog_small_image/public/52059417438_1c5142f4db_c.jpg?itok=VdDY11ng" width="300" height="200" alt="" /></div>
      <div class="span8">
        
        <div class="row-fluid field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden clearfix">
    <div class="field-items">
    
        
          <div class="field-item">
